Feature: Twitch Search # features/twitch/search.feature:1

  @browse_video
  Scenario: Verify if user is able to play searched video  # features/twitch/search.feature:4
    Given user navigates to "https://m.twitch.tv"          # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:9
    And user clicks search icon                            # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:16
    And user searches for "StarCraft II" in search bar     # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:22
    And clicks "Channels" tab from search results          # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:29
    And user scrolls the page "2" times                    # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:35
    And user selects a random streamer                     # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:41
    Then video is played on selected streamer              # steps/twitch/twitch_steps.py:48

